{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"In 2007,"},{"time":2000,"text":"I decided that we needed to reconceptualize"},{"time":4000,"text":"how we thought about economic development."},{"time":6000,"text":"Our new goal should be"},{"time":8000,"text":"that when every family thinks about where they want to live and work,"},{"time":11000,"text":"they should be able to choose between"},{"time":13000,"text":"at least a handful"},{"time":15000,"text":"of different cities"},{"time":17000,"text":"that were all competing to attract new residents."},{"time":20000,"text":"Now we're a long way away from that goal right now."},{"time":23000,"text":"There are billions of people in developing countries"},{"time":26000,"text":"who don't have even a single city that would be willing to welcome them."},{"time":29000,"text":"But the amazing thing about cities"},{"time":31000,"text":"is they're worth so much more"},{"time":33000,"text":"than it costs to build them."},{"time":35000,"text":"So we could easily supply the world"},{"time":38000,"text":"with dozens, maybe hundreds,"},{"time":40000,"text":"of new cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"Now this might sound preposterous to you"},{"time":44000,"text":"if you've never thought about new cities."},{"time":46000,"text":"But just substitute apartment building for cities."},{"time":48000,"text":"Imagine half the people who wanted to be in apartments already had them;"},{"time":51000,"text":"the other half aren't there yet."},{"time":53000,"text":"You could try and expand the capacity"},{"time":56000,"text":"by doing additions on all the existing apartments."},{"time":59000,"text":"But you know what you'd run into"},{"time":61000,"text":"is those apartments and the surrounding areas"},{"time":63000,"text":"have rules to avoid discomfort"},{"time":65000,"text":"and the distractions of construction."},{"time":68000,"text":"So it's extremely hard to do all of those additions."},{"time":70000,"text":"But you could go out someplace brand new,"},{"time":72000,"text":"build a brand new apartment building,"},{"time":75000,"text":"as long as the rules there"},{"time":77000,"text":"were ones that facilitated construction"},{"time":79000,"text":"rather than getting in the way."},{"time":81000,"text":"So I proposed"},{"time":83000,"text":"that governments create new reform zones"},{"time":86000,"text":"big enough to hold cities"},{"time":88000,"text":"and gave them a name: charter cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"Later I learned that at about this same time,"},{"time":93000,"text":"Javier and Octavio"},{"time":95000,"text":"were thinking about the challenge of reform"},{"time":97000,"text":"in Honduras."},{"time":99000,"text":"They knew that about 75,000 Hondurans every year"},{"time":103000,"text":"would leave to go to the United States,"},{"time":105000,"text":"and they wanted to ask, what could they do"},{"time":107000,"text":"to make sure that those people could stay"},{"time":109000,"text":"and do the same things in Honduras."},{"time":112000,"text":"At one point, Javier said to Octavio,"},{"time":114000,"text":"\"What if we took some of our empty land --"},{"time":116000,"text":"what if we just gave it to an embassy --"},{"time":118000,"text":"give some to the U.S. embassy; give some to the Canadian embassy --"},{"time":121000,"text":"and then if people want to go work"},{"time":123000,"text":"under the rules of Canada or under the rules of the United States,"},{"time":125000,"text":"they can go get jobs,"},{"time":127000,"text":"do everything they do on those embassy grounds"},{"time":129000,"text":"that they would otherwise have to go to Canada or the U.S. to do?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":134000,"text":"In the summer of 2009,"},{"time":136000,"text":"Honduras went through a wrenching constitutional crisis."},{"time":139000,"text":"At the next regularly scheduled election,"},{"time":142000,"text":"Pepe Lobo won in a landslide"},{"time":144000,"text":"on a platform that promised reform,"},{"time":147000,"text":"but reconciliation as well."},{"time":150000,"text":"He asked Octavio to be his chief of staff."},{"time":154000,"text":"Meanwhile, I was getting ready"},{"time":156000,"text":"to give a talk at TEDGlobal."},{"time":158000,"text":"Through a process of refinement,"},{"time":160000,"text":"trial and error, a lot of user testing,"},{"time":163000,"text":"I tried to boil this complicated concept of charter city"},{"time":166000,"text":"down to the bare essentials."},{"time":170000,"text":"The first point was the importance of rules,"},{"time":172000,"text":"like those rules that say"},{"time":174000,"text":"you can't come in and disturb all the existing apartment holders."},{"time":177000,"text":"We pay a lot of attention to new technologies,"},{"time":179000,"text":"but it takes technologies and rules to get progress,"},{"time":182000,"text":"and it's usually the rules that hold us back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"In the fall of 2010, a friend from Guatemala"},{"time":189000,"text":"sent Octavio a link to the TEDTalk."},{"time":192000,"text":"He showed it to Javier."},{"time":194000,"text":"They called me."},{"time":196000,"text":"They said, \"Let's present this to the leaders of our country.\""},{"time":199000,"text":"So in December we met in Miami,"},{"time":202000,"text":"in a hotel conference room."},{"time":204000,"text":"I tried to explain this point"},{"time":206000,"text":"about how valuable cities are,"},{"time":208000,"text":"how much more valuable they are than they cost."},{"time":210000,"text":"And I used this slide"},{"time":212000,"text":"showing how valuable the raw land is"},{"time":214000,"text":"in a place like New York City:"},{"time":216000,"text":"notice, land that's worth thousands of dollars, in some cases,"},{"time":219000,"text":"per square meter."},{"time":221000,"text":"But it was a fairly abstract discussion,"},{"time":224000,"text":"and at some point when there was a pause,"},{"time":227000,"text":"Octavio said,"},{"time":229000,"text":"\"Paul, maybe we could watch the TEDTalk.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"(Laughing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"So the TEDTalk laid out in very simple terms,"},{"time":237000,"text":"a charter city is a place"},{"time":239000,"text":"where you start with uninhabited land,"},{"time":242000,"text":"a charter that specifies the rules that will apply there"},{"time":245000,"text":"and then a chance for people to opt in,"},{"time":247000,"text":"to go live under those rules or not."},{"time":251000,"text":"So I was asked by the president of Honduras"},{"time":254000,"text":"who said that we need to do this project,"},{"time":256000,"text":"this is important,"},{"time":258000,"text":"this could be the way forward for our country."},{"time":261000,"text":"I was asked to come to Tegucigalpa"},{"time":263000,"text":"and talk again on January fourth and fifth."},{"time":266000,"text":"So I presented"},{"time":268000,"text":"another fact-filled lecture"},{"time":270000,"text":"that included a slide like this,"},{"time":272000,"text":"which tried to make the point that, if you want to create a lot of value in a city,"},{"time":275000,"text":"it has to be very big."},{"time":277000,"text":"This is a picture of Denver,"},{"time":279000,"text":"and the outline is the new airport that was built in Denver."},{"time":281000,"text":"This airport alone"},{"time":283000,"text":"covers more than 100 square kilometers."},{"time":285000,"text":"So I was trying to persuade the Hondurans,"},{"time":287000,"text":"if you build a new city,"},{"time":289000,"text":"you've got to start with a site that's at least 1,000 square kilometers."},{"time":292000,"text":"That's more than 250 hundred-thousand acres."},{"time":298000,"text":"Everybody applauded politely."},{"time":300000,"text":"The faces in the audience"},{"time":302000,"text":"were very serious and attentive."},{"time":305000,"text":"The leader of the congress came up on stage and said,"},{"time":308000,"text":"\"Professor Romer, thank you very much for your lecture,"},{"time":311000,"text":"but maybe we could watch the TEDTalk."},{"time":314000,"text":"I've got it here on my laptop.\""},{"time":318000,"text":"So I sat down, and they played the TEDTalk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321000,"text":"And it got to the essence,"},{"time":323000,"text":"which is that a new city could offer new choices for people."},{"time":326000,"text":"There would be a choice of a city which you could go to"},{"time":328000,"text":"which could be in Honduras,"},{"time":330000,"text":"instead of hundreds of miles away in the North."},{"time":332000,"text":"And it also involved new choices for leaders."},{"time":334000,"text":"Because the leaders in the government there in Honduras"},{"time":337000,"text":"would need help from partner countries,"},{"time":339000,"text":"who could benefit from partner countries"},{"time":341000,"text":"who help them set up the rules in this charter and the enforcement,"},{"time":344000,"text":"so everybody can trust"},{"time":346000,"text":"that the charter really will be enforced."},{"time":349000,"text":"And the insight of President Lobo"},{"time":351000,"text":"was that that assurance of enforcement"},{"time":354000,"text":"that I was thinking about"},{"time":356000,"text":"as a way to get the foreign investors to come in and build the city"},{"time":359000,"text":"could be equally important for all the different parties in Honduras"},{"time":362000,"text":"who had suffered for so many years"},{"time":364000,"text":"from fear and distrust."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"We went and looked at a site."},{"time":368000,"text":"This picture's from there."},{"time":370000,"text":"It easily could hold a thousand square kilometers."},{"time":373000,"text":"And shortly thereafter, on January 19th,"},{"time":376000,"text":"they voted in the congress to amend their constitution"},{"time":379000,"text":"to have a constitutional provision"},{"time":381000,"text":"that allows for special development regions."},{"time":383000,"text":"In a country which had just gone through this wrenching crisis,"},{"time":386000,"text":"the vote in the congress in favor of this constitutional amendment"},{"time":389000,"text":"was 124 to one."},{"time":392000,"text":"All parties, all factions in society, backed this."},{"time":395000,"text":"To be part of the constitution, you actually have to pass it twice in the congress."},{"time":398000,"text":"On February 17th they passed it again"},{"time":401000,"text":"with another vote of 114 to one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404000,"text":"Immediately after that vote,"},{"time":406000,"text":"on February 21st to the 24th,"},{"time":409000,"text":"a delegation of about 30 Hondurans"},{"time":411000,"text":"went to the two places in the world"},{"time":413000,"text":"that are most interested in getting into the city building business."},{"time":415000,"text":"One is South Korea."},{"time":417000,"text":"This is a picture of a big, new city center"},{"time":419000,"text":"that's being built in South Korea --"},{"time":421000,"text":"bigger than downtown Boston."},{"time":423000,"text":"Everything you see there was built in four years,"},{"time":425000,"text":"after they spent four years getting the permits."},{"time":429000,"text":"The other place that's very interested in city building is Singapore."},{"time":431000,"text":"They've actually built two cities already in China"},{"time":433000,"text":"and are preparing the third."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"So if you think about this practically,"},{"time":437000,"text":"here's where we are."},{"time":439000,"text":"They've got a site; they're already thinking about this site for the second city."},{"time":442000,"text":"They're putting in place a legal system"},{"time":444000,"text":"that could allow for managers to come in,"},{"time":446000,"text":"and also an external legal system."},{"time":448000,"text":"One country has already volunteered to let its supreme court"},{"time":451000,"text":"be the court of final appeal for the new judicial system there."},{"time":454000,"text":"There's designers and builders of cities"},{"time":456000,"text":"who are very interested."},{"time":458000,"text":"They even can bring with them some financing."},{"time":460000,"text":"But the one thing you know they've already solved"},{"time":462000,"text":"is that there's lots of tenants."},{"time":464000,"text":"There's lots of businesses that would like to locate in the Americas,"},{"time":467000,"text":"especially in a place with a free trade zone,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and there's lots of people who'd like to go there."},{"time":472000,"text":"Around the world, there's 700 million people"},{"time":474000,"text":"who say they'd like to move permanently someplace else right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477000,"text":"There's a million a year"},{"time":479000,"text":"who leave Latin America to go to the United States."},{"time":481000,"text":"Many of these are a father"},{"time":483000,"text":"who has to leave his family behind to go get a job --"},{"time":485000,"text":"sometimes a single mother"},{"time":487000,"text":"who has to get enough money to even pay for food or clothing."},{"time":490000,"text":"Sadly, sometimes there are even children"},{"time":492000,"text":"who are trying to get reunited with their parents"},{"time":494000,"text":"that they haven't seen, in some cases, for a decade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499000,"text":"So what kind of an idea is it"},{"time":501000,"text":"to think about building a brand new city in Honduras?"},{"time":503000,"text":"Or to build a dozen of these,"},{"time":505000,"text":"or a hundred of these, around the world?"},{"time":507000,"text":"What kind of an idea is it"},{"time":509000,"text":"to think about insisting"},{"time":511000,"text":"that every family have a choice of several cities"},{"time":514000,"text":"that are competing to attract new residents?"},{"time":517000,"text":"This is an idea worth spreading."},{"time":520000,"text":"And my friends from Honduras"},{"time":522000,"text":"asked me to say thank you, TED."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}